class.rdfs:comment: An organization identifier as defined in ISO 6523(-1). Note that many existing organization identifiers such as [leiCode](http://schema.org/leiCode), [duns](http://schema.org/duns) and [vatID](http://schema.org/vatID) can be expressed as an ISO 6523 identifier by setting the ICD part of the ISO 6523 identifier accordingly.
class.rdfs:label: iso6523Code
